Rulings.HAT:
● This can negate a Synchro Summon, Xyz Summon, or the Special Summon of Cyber Dragon by its own procedure.
● This can't negate a monster being Summoned by a card effect, such as by “Call of the Haunted”.
● This can't negate the Summon of a monster being Summoned by a lingering effect, like “W Nebula Meteorite".
